121
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,319
Your life and death

122
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:10,879
are controlled by me.

123
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,079
I

124
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,120
