133
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:45,279
my sister and I

134
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,639
will live in harmony.

135
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,120
Yanshu,

136
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:50,040
you will not understand.

137
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:52,040
Parents' love for their child

138
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:55,000
knows no bounds.

139
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,120
I understand.

140
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,079
This...

141
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,240
For this unworthy daughter,

142
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,160
you even used yourself as bait.

143
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,959
What a pity.

144
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,879
I know quite a bit of medicine.

145
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,480
I am afraid I will disappoint you.

146
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:29,720
Mother.

147
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,040
What should we do?

148
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,480
His Majesty arrives.

149
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,679
Father.

150
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,480
Father, they...

151
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,679
Father.

152
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:44,480
I...

153
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,679
Your Majesty.

154
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:50,600
Why did you punish me
without asking any questions?

155
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:52,080
Wouldn't I know

156
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,759
my daughter?

157
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,120
Am I not your daughter?

158
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,159
Father.

159
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,840
Have you ever cared about me?

160
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,799
I am the supreme princess

161
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:05,799
who should receive
all the love in the world.

162
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:08,519
But why have you never cared about me

163
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,879
and never believe what I say?

164
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,679
I only trust my own judgment.

165
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,120
Guards!

166
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,399
Take her

167
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,360
away!

168
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,200
Your Majesty.

169
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,360
Please calm down.

170
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,639
Your Majesty.

171
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:22,000
I was the one

172
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,679
who poisoned her.

173
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,200
It has nothing to do with Fuyu.

174
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,559
Your Majesty,

175
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:29,000
for the sake of our many years
of marriage,

176
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,600
spare Fuyu.

177
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,360
Mother.

178
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,799
It has nothing to do with Fuyu.

179
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,840
Is what your mother said

180
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,519
